            <title>[LU-3103] linkea_entry_pack is both static and exported</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3103</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;linkea_entry_pack was accidentally both declared static and explicitly exported.  That breaks the build on ppc64.&lt;/p&gt;

